# Vasati — Full Platform Build

## Phase 1: Infrastructure & Scaffolding
- [ ] 1. Scaffold repository structure (all directories, empty __init__.py files)
- [ ] 2. Write docker-compose.yml, Dockerfiles, nginx.conf, .env.example, Makefile
- [ ] 3. Write requirements.txt and requirements.dev.txt
- [ ] 4. Run `make up` — verify all services healthy

## Phase 2: Django Core Setup
- [ ] 5. Set up Django project with django-tenants (settings/base.py, urls.py, wsgi.py, celery.py)
- [ ] 6. Configure SHARED_APPS and TENANT_APPS per specification
- [ ] 7. Run migrate_schemas --shared, verify public schema in PostgreSQL

## Phase 3: Tenant & Account Apps
