- [ ] 9. Provision test org, verify schema created in PostgreSQL
- [ ] 10. Build apps/accounts — User model, OTPCode, OrgMembership
- [ ] 11. Wire up SimpleJWT + OTP auth flow (request-otp → verify-otp → JWT)
- [ ] 12. Run schema isolation test

